divs: Sighting DetailsAt 7:19pm I had just arrived home and happen to have my camera with me, a Canon Rebel T1i with an 18-55mm lens. I saw a beautiful sunset and decided to take some pictures. I was standing at the gateway entrance of my house when I started taking a few shots. I came inside my home and downloaded the pics to my laptop. I suddenly noticed that in one of my shots it reveals a dark, round shaped object within the clouds and a passanger airliner flying way below it. What's funny is that I originally bought this camera because at night I see many lights in the sky on different nights and I wanted a high power camera to catch them. I wasn't trying to take picture of a ufo but then again this is not the first time this has happen to me. It's like they want me to see them.
